analysis.description: EthCashonline.payout (/unique_chucks/7/0x0135c9a7bff72aa26e1d105ff5000e454e4dde7a.sol#191-220) allows anyone to destruct the contract
EthCashonline.payoutSelf (/unique_chucks/7/0x0135c9a7bff72aa26e1d105ff5000e454e4dde7a.sol#220-243) allows anyone to destruct the contract
EthCashonline.bytesToAddress (/unique_chucks/7/0x0135c9a7bff72aa26e1d105ff5000e454e4dde7a.sol#244-247) is declared view but contains assembly code

EthCashonline.fallback (/unique_chucks/7/0x0135c9a7bff72aa26e1d105ff5000e454e4dde7a.sol#146-191) uses a dangerous strict equality:
	- user.deposits == 1

EthCashonline.payout has external calls inside a loop:
	- addr.transfer(amount) (/unique_chucks/7/0x0135c9a7bff72aa26e1d105ff5000e454e4dde7a.sol#216-217)
